trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"> </xref> objetos no <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"> </xref> controlo.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The RepeaterItemCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> objects, which in turn represent the data items in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control.
trans-unit.target: A classe de RepeaterItemCollection representa uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>objetos, que por sua vez representam os itens de dados num <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>controlo.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>

trans-unit.source: To programmatically retrieve <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> objects from a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control, use one of the following methods: - Use the indexer to get a single <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> object from the collection using array notation.
trans-unit.target: Para obter programaticamente <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>objetos de uma <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>controlar, utilize um dos seguintes métodos:-Utilize o indexador para obter um único <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>objeto da coleção utilizando a notação de matriz.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.CopyTo%2A> method to copy the contents of the collection to a <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Utilize o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.CopyTo%2A>método para copiar o conteúdo da coleção para um <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>objeto, que, em seguida, pode ser utilizado para obter os itens da coleção.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A> method to create an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> interface, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Utilize o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>método para criar um <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>interface, o que, em seguida, pode ser utilizado para obter os itens da coleção.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use `foreach` (C#) or `For Each` (Visual Basic) to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Utilizar `foreach` (c#) ou `For Each` (Visual Basic) para iterar através da coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.Count%2A> property specifies the total number of items in the collection and is commonly used to determine the upper bound of the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.Count%2A>propriedade especifica o número total de itens na coleção e costuma ser utilizada para determinar o limite superior da coleção.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"> </xref> que contém os itens com a qual ao inicializar a coleção.

trans-unit.source: Copies all the items from this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"></xref> to the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, starting at the specified index in the <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to copy the contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection> into the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, starting at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Utilize este método para copiar o conteúdo do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>especificado em <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>objeto, que começa no índice especificado.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The `array` parameter must be a zero-based <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object.

trans-unit.target: Um baseado em zero <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> que recebe os itens copiados do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move to the next item in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Utilize o <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>método para mover para o seguinte item na coleção.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator back to the initial position.
trans-unit.target: Utilize o <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>método para mover o enumerador de volta para a posição inicial.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > After you create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> object or use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator to the first item in the collection, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Depois de criar um <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>objeto ou utilize o <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>método para mover o enumerador para o primeiro item na coleção, tem de chamar o <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>método.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>
